					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13698823#post-4766587</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13698823/scp-5165#post-4766587</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 04 Sep 2020 05:31:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Grigori Karpin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558017</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I honestly think this is &quot;more than meets the eye.&quot; My first thought, based on the minimal formatting, was that this was not going to be good reading. I apologize for ever even thinking that. You take your time and slowly unfold the narrative, with a particularly somber note for the end.</p> <p>I think you could have nailed it a bit better, as it just sort of ends. But also, the subject matter is such that maybe a quiet somber ending is just right.</p> <p>Either way, what a wonderful first article. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
